{"tid":676062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川女手術麻醉後遭強姦　淫醫潛逃落網被刑拘","createTime":"2018-05-24T05:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T07:56:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b9913bf1f5788d324fc0a06ace12f85bdfaff1dd","tid":676062,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/photo/bkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180523174428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180523174428&h=79e5629f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">受害人家屬在醫院門口掛起橫額，怒批「黑醫生」強姦病人的醜行。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/photo/bkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001_02p.jpg?20180523174428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180523174428&h=21fbcbb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川成都近日爆出一名女病人到雙流恒康醫院做手術時，被注射麻醉藥後遭醫生強姦。當地警方目前已介入，涉事醫生亦已被抓獲。醫院方面則指已展開司法程序，惟家屬連日來拉起橫額到醫院抗議。雙流區公安分局於官方微博通報，指涉事的35歲醫生已在南充市落網，目前已因涉嫌強姦罪被刑事拘留。<br />\n<br />\n一則題為《病人在醫院遭強暴》的消息在微信朋友圈瘋傳，並引起高度關注。發貼者在回覆眾多查詢留言時稱，「我朋友到醫院打針被醫生用麻醉藥品麻醉了，然後把她強姦了，醫生被抓了，但是醫院不管，說他們沒有責任」。發貼者同時發布一段受害人的母親到醫院要求交代的短片，可見她情緒激動翻出1樓鐵欄外企跳，「我朋友的媽激動得要跳樓了，醫院的院長還不出來管事，真的是太氣憤了」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後有媒體採訪到27歲的受害女子，據她表示，事發於本月10日上午，當時她獨自到醫院做腋下除臭手術，當時大約麻醉了1個小時，結果醒來後發現被醫生強姦，她隨即報警，「現在我不想提這件事，這件事已經讓我很疲憊、很崩潰」。<br />\n<br />\n雙流區政府一名工作人員表示，目前已掌握事件的基本情況，並指事件屬刑事案件。據雙流區公安分局通報，10日上午9時許，該局接獲報警稱一名女子在雙流區民營恒康醫院就醫時，被醫生強姦。該局立即成立專案組調查，並於12日中午12時許在南充市儀隴縣，將疑犯羅某抓獲歸案。羅某已招認在治療室為受害人注射鎮靜劑後，趁其入睡時性侵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/bkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fbkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001.html&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6c7f1473\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/bkncn-20180523134959864-0523_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1e58d30f0f18dbd1401ac5889f216c7d45b936b0","tid":676062,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"當時她獨自到醫院做腋下除臭手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01b0cb48885881c45b4af730c42c1459955715c","tid":676062,"uid":39576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"遲d到香港...."},{"pid":"ba3aaa29ca7ecc752ea293a79b290d20ef08ea1d","tid":676062,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"蝗國又記一分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334f447504e7654fd39263a28696293ae9219fe8","tid":676062,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:55:00.000Z","msg":"唔寫明四川仲以為係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483bd35f69e9c2ae7f12f2038aeeb7df0ad895fb","tid":676062,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e58d30f0f18dbd1401ac5889f216c7d45b936b0","tid":676062,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"當時她獨自到醫院做腋下除臭手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"狐仙"},{"pid":"1561e083b4df747ecef2a505babcf8a8d0dafae9","tid":676062,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime